{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/blog/expressions-for-shortage/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Developer's blog"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"03c0b835-ccd4-5daf-ab75-4e24fd1165b6","excerpt":"Meaning This article explains expressions used to describe shortage or insufficiency, such as be short of, lack, and run low on.\nThey are used when something is…","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#meaning\">Meaning</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#grammar-and-usage\">Grammar and Usage</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#comparison-and-mapping\">Comparison and Mapping</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#common-phrases\">Common Phrases</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#collocations\">Collocations</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#examples\">Examples</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#synonyms-or-related\">Synonyms or Related</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#antonym\">Antonym</a></li>\n</ul>","html":"<h2 id=\"meaning\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#meaning\" aria-label=\"meaning permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Meaning</h2>\n<p>This article explains expressions used to describe <strong>shortage or insufficiency</strong>, such as <strong>be short of</strong>, <strong>lack</strong>, and <strong>run low on</strong>.\nThey are used when something is <strong>not enough</strong>, <strong>in short supply</strong>, or <strong>insufficient</strong> to meet a need.</p>\n<h2 id=\"grammar-and-usage\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#grammar-and-usage\" aria-label=\"grammar and usage permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Grammar and Usage</h2>\n<p>These expressions typically involve nouns referring to <strong>resources, time, money, sleep, or people</strong>.\nSome appear in the <strong>passive form</strong>, while others are active or idiomatic.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>be short of + noun</strong> → not have enough of something</li>\n<li><strong>lack + noun</strong> → be without or not have something necessary</li>\n<li><strong>run out of + noun</strong> → completely use up something</li>\n<li><strong>run low on + noun</strong> → have very little remaining</li>\n<li><strong>be deprived of + noun</strong> → be kept from having something essential</li>\n<li><strong>be in need of + noun</strong> → require or want something lacking</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Examples:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>We are <strong>short of</strong> time.</li>\n<li>She <strong>lacks</strong> confidence.</li>\n<li>They <strong>ran out of</strong> fuel.</li>\n<li>I’m <strong>running low on</strong> cash.</li>\n<li>The country is <strong>deprived of</strong> clean water.</li>\n<li>He is <strong>in need of</strong> help.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"comparison-and-mapping\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#comparison-and-mapping\" aria-label=\"comparison and mapping permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Comparison and Mapping</h2>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Expression</th>\n<th>Core Meaning</th>\n<th>Formality</th>\n<th>Typical Use</th>\n<th>Example</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>be short of</strong></td>\n<td>have less than needed; be lacking</td>\n<td>medium</td>\n<td>daily life, general</td>\n<td>I’m <strong>short of</strong> money this month.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>lack</strong></td>\n<td>not have something necessary</td>\n<td>high</td>\n<td>formal, written</td>\n<td>She <strong>lacks</strong> experience for this job.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>run out of</strong></td>\n<td>completely use up</td>\n<td>informal</td>\n<td>conversation, practical use</td>\n<td>We <strong>ran out of</strong> coffee.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>run low on</strong></td>\n<td>nearly finished, still some left</td>\n<td>informal</td>\n<td>daily life, business</td>\n<td>The printer is <strong>running low on</strong> ink.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>be deprived of</strong></td>\n<td>be denied something essential</td>\n<td>high</td>\n<td>formal, social issues</td>\n<td>Many people are <strong>deprived of</strong> basic education.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>be in need of</strong></td>\n<td>require or want something lacking</td>\n<td>medium</td>\n<td>polite, formal</td>\n<td>The shelter is <strong>in need of</strong> donations.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>be short on</strong></td>\n<td>similar to “short of,” often AmE usage</td>\n<td>informal</td>\n<td>American English</td>\n<td>I’m <strong>short on</strong> sleep lately.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>be pressed for</strong></td>\n<td>have very little time/money/resources</td>\n<td>medium–high</td>\n<td>business, time expressions</td>\n<td>We’re <strong>pressed for</strong> time before the deadline.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h2 id=\"common-phrases\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#common-phrases\" aria-label=\"common phrases permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Common Phrases</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>be short of time / money / sleep</li>\n<li>lack experience / confidence / skill</li>\n<li>run out of gas / patience / ideas</li>\n<li>run low on supplies / ink / cash</li>\n<li>be deprived of freedom / rights / food</li>\n<li>be in need of help / care / rest</li>\n<li>be short on sleep / patience</li>\n<li>be pressed for time / money</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"collocations\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#collocations\" aria-label=\"collocations permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Collocations</h2>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Verb Phrase</th>\n<th>Example</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>be short of</strong></td>\n<td>We’re <strong>short of</strong> staff today.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>lack</strong></td>\n<td>He <strong>lacks</strong> motivation to continue.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>run out of</strong></td>\n<td>They <strong>ran out of</strong> tickets for the event.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>run low on</strong></td>\n<td>The team is <strong>running low on</strong> energy.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>be deprived of</strong></td>\n<td>Children were <strong>deprived of</strong> sleep.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>be in need of</strong></td>\n<td>The hospital is <strong>in need of</strong> more equipment.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>be pressed for</strong></td>\n<td>We’re <strong>pressed for</strong> time, so let’s move quickly.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h2 id=\"examples\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#examples\" aria-label=\"examples permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Examples</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>I’m <strong>short of</strong> time today.</li>\n<li>The students <strong>lack</strong> motivation.</li>\n<li>We <strong>ran out of</strong> fuel halfway to the station.</li>\n<li>The shop is <strong>running low on</strong> stock.</li>\n<li>The victims were <strong>deprived of</strong> medical care.</li>\n<li>The organization is <strong>in need of</strong> volunteers.</li>\n<li>I’m <strong>short on</strong> sleep this week.</li>\n<li>We’re <strong>pressed for</strong> time before the meeting.</li>\n<li>The country <strong>lacks</strong> natural resources.</li>\n<li>She’s <strong>running low on</strong> patience.</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"synonyms-or-related\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#synonyms-or-related\" aria-label=\"synonyms or related permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Synonyms or Related</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>be short of</li>\n<li>lack</li>\n<li>be deficient in</li>\n<li>be low on</li>\n<li>run low on</li>\n<li>run out of</li>\n<li>be in need of</li>\n<li>be deprived of</li>\n<li>be pressed for</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"antonym\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#antonym\" aria-label=\"antonym permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Antonym</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>have plenty of</strong></li>\n<li><strong>be rich in</strong></li>\n<li><strong>be full of</strong></li>\n<li><strong>be abundant in</strong></li>\n<li><strong>have enough of</strong></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"Expressions for shortage: be short of, lack, run low on, and more","date":"2025-11-01","description":"English learning materials; expressions that mean shortage or insufficiency explained with examples.","tags":["English","phrase","verb","expression"],"featuredImage":{"publicURL":"/static/97769fa7890ad0cd2cd831527f66bed3/expressions-for-shortage.png","childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#f8e8c8","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/97769fa7890ad0cd2cd831527f66bed3/b5658/expressions-for-shortage.png","srcSet":"/static/97769fa7890ad0cd2cd831527f66bed3/acb7c/expressions-for-shortage.png 256w,\n/static/97769fa7890ad0cd2cd831527f66bed3/ccc41/expressions-for-shortage.png 512w,\n/static/97769fa7890ad0cd2cd831527f66bed3/b5658/expressions-for-shortage.png 1024w","sizes":"(min-width: 1024px) 1024px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/97769fa7890ad0cd2cd831527f66bed3/22bfc/expressions-for-shortage.webp 256w,\n/static/97769fa7890ad0cd2cd831527f66bed3/d689f/expressions-for-shortage.webp 512w,\n/static/97769fa7890ad0cd2cd831527f66bed3/67ded/expressions-for-shortage.webp 1024w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 1024px) 1024px, 100vw"}]},"width":1024,"height":1024}}}}},"relatedPosts":{"nodes":[]},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/dispute/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"dispute meaning and examples"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/impersonate/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"impersonate meaning and examples"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"03c0b835-ccd4-5daf-ab75-4e24fd1165b6","previousPostId":"171d297c-2a25-52c8-8b8a-6028c9a09b4d","nextPostId":"a2400053-0b6e-5fc5-bde2-af6f43cf7b28","relatedPosts":[]}},"staticQueryHashes":["2841359383"],"slicesMap":{}}